

<div class="fm-container" style="display: flex;flex-direction: column;background-color: #FFFFFF;width: 80%;height: 80%;margin: 0 auto;padding: 2rem 0;">
    <div class="fm-img">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgnszubi2/image/upload/v1694646013/blobs/confirm-img_h50gjv.png" height="auto" alt="image" style="display: block;margin: 0 auto;width: 90%;">
    </div>
<div class="body" style="padding: 30px 0;display: flex;flex-direction: column;width: 90%;margin: 0 auto;">
    <h4 class="title" style="font-weight: 700;font-size: 24px;line-height: 32px;font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;">Confirm your email address</h4>

    <p class="message" style="padding: 30px 0;font-family: 'Cabinet Grotesk', sans-serif;font-weight: 500;font-size: 15px;line-height: 21px;color: #969CA5;margin: 25px 0;">
        Hi <%= recipientName %>,<br><br>
        We are excited to welcome you to Farmiz.<br>
        Thank you for taking this step to help be a part of our journey and mission.<br>
        Please click the button below to confirm your email address and activate your account.
    </p>

    <p class="btn-action" style="font-family: 'Cabinet Grotesk', sans-serif;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 40px;"><a href="&lt;%= accountVerificationToken %&gt;" target="_blank" class="action-btn" style="text-decoration: none;background-color: #152108;color: #BEF263;padding: 5px 10px;border-radius: 5px;font-weight: 700;font-size: 16px;font-family: 'Cabinet Grotesk', sans-serif;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 40px;">Confirm Email Address</a></p>
</div></div>